{"tid":1291610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【鳩鐵野餐區CCTV地圖】","createTime":"2019-07-07T03:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T03:28:33.000Z","uid":268702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"918e9570cc38ead52323daa6dc8cbd69259aebfa","tid":1291610,"uid":268702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvUTQpO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvUTQpO.jpg&h=aceec7aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n野餐最緊要係食得安心盡興，但聚餐地點往往有好多CCTV moon實晒，喺監控鏡頭下大家都食得好唔安樂，所以我哋整咗個地圖方便大家野餐預算食材。<br />\n<br />\n野餐熱點野狗多，易有傳染病，任何時間都時刻記住戴返口罩保平安，注意個人安全，唔好病、唔好死。<br />\n<br />\n鳩鐵入面有大量CCTV，尤其門口同過關入閘前都有好多碌依啲放左12部CCTV嘅柱，總之如果巴絲打入得去嘅話\b，就要預左會俾人高清無死角咁影到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVF0vqZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVF0vqZ.jpg&h=59ae6a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/he8UzWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhe8UzWz.jpg&h=28e2c9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有朋友做埋九龍遊行路線嘅CCTV地圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LandscapeAtGrade/photos/a.2558676197477486/2570727626272343/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLandscapeAtGrade%2Fphotos%2Fa.2558676197477486%2F2570727626272343%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=8a172bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LandscapeAtGrade/photos/a.2558676197477486/2570727626272343/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，之前整左政總、警總、禮賓府、律政中心、會展CCTV位置地圖（將會持續更新位置、資料），之後再去野餐嘅話記得留意下<br />\n地圖link：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2RB2h5m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RB2h5m&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=2a10c4ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2RB2h5m</a>"},{"pid":"fa0b74d43f30194688bd2db5bf2069789afcd851","tid":1291610,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"哇屌 寫輪眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}